casebody.head_matter:
STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
Mark MELVIN, Defendant-Respondent.
079101
C-30 Sept. Term 2017
Supreme Court of New Jersey.
September 22, 2017
ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION.
To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:
A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003003-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;
It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
